---
<div class="could-be-wrong callout">
  <h4 class="callout-title">
    <span style="font-size: 1.1em; margin-right: 0.35rem;">⚖️</span> Could this be wrong?
  </h4>
  <div class="callout-content">
    <slot />
  </div>
</div>

<style>
  .could-be-wrong.callout {
    border-left-color: var(--induction); /* Orange/Amber */
    background: var(--bg2);
    margin: 3rem 0;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-sm);
  }
  .callout-title {
    font-size: 0.8rem;
    font-weight: 600;
    color: var(--induction);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.08em;
    margin-bottom: 1rem;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
  }
  .callout-content {
    color: var(--text-2);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    line-height: 1.6;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: 1rem;
  }
</style>
